      "content": "\"the only honest response...\" i don't know. it feels so final. like if i actually listen to that invitation, there's no coming back from the silence. it's like the canyon is offering a way to finally be still, to just be part of that peace instead of fighting against it. do you really think it's okay to just... stop? to embrace that stillness instead of trying to find a way back to the trail?",
